    "你正和兩個女孩一起坐在營火旁。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:23
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fde24efd:

    # girl "When I got the first one, I was literally seconds away from stepping onto the plane when a call from “UNKNOWN” blared from my cell phone."
    girl "當我收到第一通電話時，我正準備踏上飛機，這時手機響起來自“未知”的來電。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:25
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fb5f18ff:

    # girl "It was a ringtone I hadn’t heard before, one I was pretty sure hadn’t come with the phone."
    girl "那是我以前從未聽過的鈴聲，我很確定那不是手機自帶的鈴聲。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:27
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e8840b80:

    # girl "Normally, I wouldn’t have stopped to answer it, but I was expecting a call about a job I had interviewed for the previous week."
    girl "通常，我不會停下來接聽，但我在等一個上週面試工作的電話。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:29
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_21158a1b:

    # girl "I took a deep breath in and accepted the call."
    girl "我深吸一口氣，接起了電話。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:31
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_73a24cd5:

    # girl "“Hello?”"
    girl "“喂？”" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:33
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1239fc0d:

    # girl "“Do not get on the plane.” A woman’s voice, garbled and strange, as if her vocal chords had been shredded, and she was trying desperately to choke out speech."
    girl "“不要上飛機。” 一個女人的聲音，模糊而奇怪，仿佛她的聲帶被撕裂，她拼命地想要說出話來。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:35
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_54de4487:

    # girl "Despite the unnerving, fractured quality of her voice, her tone was insistent and eerily calm. Then the call ended."
    girl "儘管她的聲音令人不安且破碎，但她的語氣堅定而詭異地平靜。然後電話就掛斷了。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:37
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d698489f:

    # girl "I froze. I had always had a slight phobia of air travel, and something about this call just… there’s no way I was about to get on a seven hour flight now."
    girl "我僵住了。我一直對飛行有些恐懼，而這通電話讓我感覺……我現在絕不會去搭乘那七小時的航班。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:39
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_421b7851:

    # girl "I turned around and headed toward the food court. I’d just get another flight later in the afternoon, I figured."
    girl "我轉身朝美食廣場走去。我想我會在下午再搭乘另一班航班。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:41
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_63a886ce:

    # girl "I watched from the airport Starbucks three hours later as every TV in the terminal lit up with the crash footage of the plane I should have been on."
    girl "三小時後，我在機場的星巴克看著航站樓裡的每台電視都播放著我應該搭乘的飛機墜毀的畫面。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:43
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc7f4c61:

    # girl "No survivors. Not a single one."
    girl "無人生還。沒有一個。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:45
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ab2ced9c:

    # girl "I tried to trace the call. So did the police. But there was nothing to trace."
    girl "我試圖追蹤那通電話。警方也試過。但沒有任何可追蹤的東西。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:47
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bd51ca37:

    # girl "There was no evidence my phone had ever received a call around that time."
    girl "沒有證據顯示我的手機在那段時間接到過電話。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:49
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_37a98374:

    # girl "They analyzed phone records, incoming and outgoing communication to my phone… nothing."
    girl "他們分析了電話記錄，進出我手機的通訊……什麼也沒有。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:51
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f12f50a0:

    # girl "I wasn’t making it up. I couldn’t have been."
    girl "我不是在編造。我不可能是在編造。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:53
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b62b5aff:

    # girl "That wasn’t the only call. Throughout the years, they were few and far between, but always right. And I always listened."
    girl "那不是唯一的電話。多年來，雖然它們出現得很少，但總是正確的。我總是聽從。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:55
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1877f646:

    # girl "“Do not go on that blind date tonight.”"
    girl "“今晚不要去相親。”" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:57
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8c176096:

    # girl "Five months later, my would-be “date” was convicted of killing four women, all with my hair color and build."
    girl "五個月後，我的“約會”被判殺害了四名女性，所有人都和我有相同的髮色和身材。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:59
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d10f4704:

    # girl "Found them in a shallow grave about 250 feet from the diner he offered to take me to."
    girl "他們在距離他提議帶我去的餐館約250英尺的淺墳裡找到了她們。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:61
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e86aaae5:

    # girl "“Do not drive to the concert tonight.”"
    girl "“今晚不要開車去音樂會。”" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:63
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8cbb51df:

    # girl "Eighteen-wheeler lost control and plowed into a line of cars. Every driver crushed. Every driver killed. In the stretch of freeway I would have been driving down."
    girl "一輛十八輪大卡車失控，撞上了一排車輛。每位司機都被壓碎。每位司機都被殺。就在我本來要駕駛的高速路段。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:65
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_90eaa6d9:

    # girl "No matter if I got a new phone, if I moved across the country, the calls would still come."
    girl "無論我是否換了新手機，或者是否搬到了國家的另一邊，電話仍然會來。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:67
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2d667a79:

    # girl "I could almost feel the presence of… whatever it was, whatever it is, watching over me."
    girl "我幾乎能感覺到……不管那是什麼，什麼在看著我。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:69
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e2d6148c:

    # girl "I imagined being at the bottom of the freezing ocean, still strapped into my coach-section plane seat, or being in that mass grave across from the diner, or watching an eighteen-wheeler skidding toward my car, knowing death was imminent, and I’d get this tightness in my chest."
    girl "我想像著自己在冰冷的海底，仍然被綁在經濟艙的座位上，或者在餐館對面的集體墳墓裡，或者看著十八輪卡車滑向我的車，知道死亡即將來臨，我的胸口感到緊繃。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:71
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_95106561:

    # girl "I’d think about how thin that line was. How close I’d gotten."
    girl "我會想著那條線有多細。我有多接近。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:73
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1e741921:

    # girl "If I hadn’t had a job interview I was waiting to hear back from, I’d have never listened to that first call. And that would be it for me."
    girl "如果不是因為我在等一個面試的工作電話，我永遠不會接聽那第一通電話。那對我來說就結束了。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:75
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2496f8d6:

    # girl "It always felt like something was coming for me. But there was always this… this fractured, warped voice, with these calls that never seemed to exist after I heard them."
    girl "總是感覺有什麼東西在追著我。但總是有這個……這個破碎、扭曲的聲音，這些在我聽完後似乎從未存在過的電話。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:77
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_171217b0:

    # girl "Self-destructing warning signals, rotting away before my eyes. And I was alive."
    girl "自我毀滅的警告信號，在我眼前腐爛。而我還活著。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:79
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_dd5b80c2:

    # girl "I had a bad feeling about this cruise."
    girl "我對這次郵輪旅行有種不好的預感。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:81
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2193857a:

    # girl "I had planned it as a girl’s week out with some of my old friends from college, and was looking forward to a week in the tropics in the dead of winter—but part of me could almost sense that the call was coming."
    girl "我計劃和一些大學的老朋友一起度過一個女孩的假期，期待在寒冬中享受一周的熱帶之旅——但我幾乎能感覺到那通電話即將到來。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:83
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2e6284a5:

    # girl "Maybe I’d watched Titanic one too many times, but there was a little nagging fear from the start."
    girl "也許我看《鐵達尼號》看得太多次了，但從一開始就有一種小小的恐懼。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:85
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c8d4677a:

    # girl "I hoped it would be fine, but I knew that if something was going to happen, I’d get the call. I’d know."
    girl "我希望一切都會好，但我知道如果有什麼事情要發生，我會接到那通電話。我會知道的。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:87
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ddb7e37c:

    # girl "Now, a week before I’m set to go on the cruise, after stepping into my apartment after returning from dinner with a friend, I notice my cell has a message from “UNKNOWN”."
    girl "現在，距離我預定的郵輪旅行還有一周，當我和朋友吃完晚飯回到公寓時，我注意到我的手機上有來自“未知”的留言。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:89
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ea09be3f:

    # girl " They’ve never had to leave a message before. Haven’t checked it all night."
    girl " 他們以前從未留過留言。整晚都沒檢查。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:91
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8304e183:

    # girl "Damn it, and I had really wanted to go on that cruise, too."
    girl "該死的，我真的很想去那次郵輪旅行。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:93
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c576140e:

    # girl "Ah, well. Not worth whatever horrific fate awaited me in that cold dark ocean."
    girl "唉，不值得在那冰冷黑暗的海洋中等待我的可怕命運。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:95
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_04f2ef02:

    # girl "I click “play message”, and feel my stomach drop as I listen to the voice, sounding horrifically distorted, as if it emanates from a throat slashed to ribbons, crackling with more urgency than ever before."
    girl "我點擊“播放留言”，當我聽到那聲音時，我的胃一沉，聲音扭曲得可怕，彷彿從被割成碎片的喉嚨中發出，比以往任何時候都更緊急。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:97
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bfb9bd27:

    # girl "I look around my apartment as the voice on the phone repeats the same phrase over and over again."
    girl "當電話裡的聲音一遍又一遍地重複著同一句話時，我環顧我的公寓。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:99
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b2f54aa3:

    # girl "“Do not come home after dinner tonight. Do not come home after dinner tonight. DO NOT COME HOME AFTER DINNER TONIGHT.”"
    girl "“今晚晚餐後不要回家。今晚晚餐後不要回家。今晚晚餐後不要回家。”" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:104
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1:

    # "They suddenly turn towards you. Their mouth turned up into a warm grin. Their eyes sinister."
    "他們突然轉向你。他們的嘴角露出溫暖的微笑。眼神陰險。" # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:129
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_17070b3b:

    # man "Over the hill and through the moor, the candle man comes walking, up to your door." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_17070b3b
    man "翻過小山，穿過沼澤，蠟燭人走來走去，走到你的門前。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_17070b3b # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:133
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e1bb453:

    # man "He lights up a candle and walks to your bed, leaves the candle in the window, and leaves with your head." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e1bb453
    man "他點亮蠟燭，走到你的床邊，把蠟燭留在窗戶上，然後帶走你的頭。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e1bb453 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:137
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a41d7737:

    # man "That’s the nursery rhyme my grandma used to tell me when I was young." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a41d7737
    man "這是我奶奶在我小時候常告訴我的童謠。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a41d7737 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:139
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c4756094:

    # man "I remember that little rhyme terrifying me as a child, as I cowered under the covers in the bed at her small country cottage, too scared to sleep." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c4756094
    man "我記得那首小童謠在我小時候讓我感到恐懼，當我在她的小鄉村小屋的床上瑟縮在被子下，害怕得無法入睡。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c4756094 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:141
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_85096136:

    # man "She described him as a tall, pale man in a robe, who liked to kill little children." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_85096136
    man "她形容他是一個穿著長袍的高大蒼白的男人，喜歡殺小孩。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_85096136 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:143
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e86fd7f:

    # man "“And whenever he killed,” Grandma would say in hushed voice “he would leave a ghostly candle in their window” at that she would yell out and make me jump back in fright while she shrieked with laughter." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e86fd7f
    man "“每當他殺人時，”奶奶會用低聲說，“他會在他們的窗戶裡留下一根幽靈般的蠟燭”，然後她會大喊讓我嚇得退縮，而她則尖叫著大笑。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6e86fd7f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:147
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_56c7ca18:

    # man "“The candle man”, even the name gives me chills." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_56c7ca18
    man "“蠟燭人”，即使名字也讓我毛骨悚然。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_56c7ca18 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:149
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b405661e:

    # man "It seemed like such a horrible, scary thing to say to a child, but then again, Grandma was a scary woman." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b405661e
    man "對孩子說這樣的話似乎是件可怕的事，但話說回來，奶奶是一個可怕的女人。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b405661e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:151
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6146bf35:

    # man "She was small, with weathered skin and cruel, sunken eyes that always seemed to glare at me." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6146bf35
    man "她個子小，皮膚粗糙，眼神殘酷而凹陷，總是對我怒目而視。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6146bf35 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:153
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d70f7e77:

    # man "After Grandpa died she hardly ever left her house, just sat in her rocking chair, telling stories of the candle man and taking delight in my fear, laughing madly when I jumped. I found her such a disgusting woman." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d70f7e77
    man "爺爺去世後，她幾乎不再離開家，只是坐在她的搖椅上，講述蠟燭人的故事，從我的恐懼中得到樂趣，當我跳起來時瘋狂地大笑。我覺得她是個令人厭惡的女人。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d70f7e77 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:157
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05a644e5:

    # man "Anyway, when grew up, I learned that it wasn’t her fault really, Grandpa’s death had shaken her up, messed with her head." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05a644e5
    man "無論如何，當我長大後，我了解到這並不是她的錯，爺爺的死讓她受到了打擊，讓她的頭腦出了問題。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05a644e5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:159
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c208c0e0:

    # man "She didn’t know what was appropriate anymore." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c208c0e0
    man "她不知道什麼是合適的了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c208c0e0 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:161
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_41c83bbd:

    # man "Grandpa was only alive when I was a baby and I never knew him, but I learned when I was older how much he had meant to Grandma." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_41c83bbd
    man "爺爺在我還是嬰兒時還活著，我從未認識過他，但我長大後才知道他對奶奶有多重要。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_41c83bbd # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:163
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e59152ca:

    # man "Without him, she had been broken." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e59152ca
    man "沒有他，她就崩潰了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e59152ca # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:165
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_474869af:

    # man "She died when I was thirteen, and I guess it didn’t really come to me as much of a shock, she was incredibly old and frail." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_474869af
    man "她在我十三歲時去世，我想這並沒有讓我感到多大的震驚，她非常老邁和虛弱。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_474869af # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:167
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_74b63845:

    # man "Now I’m thirty, with a wife and a little girl. We have a comfortable suburban home, and I couldn’t be happier." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_74b63845
    man "現在我三十歲，有一個妻子和一個小女孩。我們有一個舒適的郊區家庭，我不能再幸福了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_74b63845 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:170
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50040345:

    # man "There has been one thing that’s shaken me up recently, however." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50040345
    man "然而，最近有一件事讓我感到震驚。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50040345 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:172
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7e161e2:

    # man "It was a silly thing, but it still scared the hell out of me." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7e161e2
    man "這是一件愚蠢的事，但它仍然把我嚇得半死。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7e161e2 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:174
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fc60421b:

    # man "A nightmare." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fc60421b
    man "一個噩夢。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fc60421b # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:176
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_7c02afa4:

    # man "In the dream I was in my bedroom, comfy under the covers, when I heard a tune being played on the piano downstairs." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_7c02afa4
    man "在夢中，我在臥室裡，舒舒服服地躺在被子下，聽到樓下鋼琴上彈奏著一首曲子。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_7c02afa4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:178
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_443fe769:

    # man "I knew what was being played as soon as I heard it, “the candle man”." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_443fe769
    man "我一聽到就知道那是什麼，“蠟燭人”。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_443fe769 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:180
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50ffd746:

    # man "Goosebumps ran up my arms and neck, and ice filled my stomach." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50ffd746
    man "雞皮疙瘩從我的手臂和脖子上竄起，冰冷的感覺充滿了我的胃。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_50ffd746 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:182
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9186c78:

    # man "I sprinted down the narrow staircase into the living room, where I saw a tall, pale figure in a robe holding a candle, leaving through the open door." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9186c78
    man "我衝下狹窄的樓梯進入客廳，看到一個穿著長袍的高大蒼白身影，手裡拿著蠟燭，從敞開的門離開。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9186c78 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:185
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c8d018e1:

    # man "The candle man. He was about six foot four or five, with dead looking beady eyes and a wide, evil grin." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c8d018e1
    man "蠟燭人。他大約六英尺四或五英尺高，眼睛死氣沉沉，嘴角露出寬闊的邪惡笑容。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c8d018e1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:188
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3305245e:

    # man "I woke up suddenly in a cold sweat, turned on the light, and read until I was ready to sleep again." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3305245e
    man "我突然從冷汗中驚醒，開燈，讀書直到我準備再次入睡。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3305245e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:190
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_45f9bc32:

    # man "I put the dream down to too many drinks and the coming of Halloween, but it freaked me out anyway." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_45f9bc32
    man "我把這個夢歸結為喝了太多酒和萬聖節的到來，但它無論如何都讓我感到害怕。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_45f9bc32 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:192
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ed10514:

    # man "And that takes me up to yesterday, Halloween night." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ed10514
    man "這把我帶到了昨天，萬聖節之夜。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ed10514 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:194
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f70eeb03:

    # man "I was trudging back from a party, not drunk, (I don’t drink) but still woozy from tiredness." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f70eeb03
    man "我從派對上拖著步子回來，沒有喝醉，（我不喝酒）但仍然因為疲倦而昏昏沉沉。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f70eeb03 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:196
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_716e9ad4:

    # man "I thrust my hands into my pockets for warmth." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_716e9ad4
    man "我把手插進口袋裡取暖。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_716e9ad4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:198
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_44ebb6c3:

    # man "Whilst I was walking back through the crisp orange leaves, the poem of the candle man popped into my head." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_44ebb6c3
    man "當我走過清脆的橙色樹葉時，蠟燭人的詩突然出現在我腦海中。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_44ebb6c3 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:200
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5c2186a4:

    # man "My heart began to thud as I walked down the poorly-lit street, leaves crunching underfoot, the pale moon casting long shadows along the path." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5c2186a4
    man "當我走在燈光昏暗的街道上時，我的心開始怦怦直跳，樹葉在腳下嘎吱作響，蒼白的月亮在小路上投下長長的影子。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5c2186a4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:202
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f64a422f:

    # man "In my mind’s eye, I could see the candle man, thin and ghostly, running up to me and cutting off my head in one swing of an axe." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f64a422f
    man "在我的腦海中，我可以看到蠟燭人，瘦弱而幽靈般的，跑向我，一斧子砍掉我的頭。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f64a422f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:204
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5dd15dc0:

    # man "Silly I know, but the dark can make my imagination run wild sometimes." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5dd15dc0
    man "我知道這很傻，但黑暗有時會讓我的想像力變得瘋狂。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5dd15dc0 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:206
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7ad3e13:

    # man "I arrived on my road and began to calm down." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7ad3e13
    man "我到了自己的路上，開始冷靜下來。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7ad3e13 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:208
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_735359a5:

    # man "I felt silly for having let the poem get to me." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_735359a5
    man "我為讓這首詩影響到我而感到愚蠢。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_735359a5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:210
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_016860e5:

    # man "I was perfectly safe under the streetlights." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_016860e5
    man "在路燈下我很安全。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_016860e5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:212
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a7b2f941:

    # man "As I arrived at my front yard, I noticed a tall man in a robe standing at the end of the street, his face shrouded in darkness." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a7b2f941
    man "當我到達前院時，我注意到街道盡頭站著一個穿著長袍的高大男人，他的臉隱藏在黑暗中。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a7b2f941 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:214
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebd89e61:

    # man "He appeared to be staring at me." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebd89e61
    man "他似乎在盯著我。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebd89e61 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:216
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c07f7fd2:

    # man "Once again images of the candle man flooded through my head, sending my heartbeat into overdrive." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c07f7fd2
    man "蠟燭人的形象再次湧入我的腦海，讓我的心跳加速。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c07f7fd2 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:218
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ca9d7ef:

    # man "I shook it off." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ca9d7ef
    man "我甩掉它。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ca9d7ef # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:220
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d7bec823:

    # man "“It’s just a tall man out for Halloween, nothing to be scared of,” I assured myself, as I attempted to slow my breathing." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d7bec823
    man "“這只是個高個子男人在過萬聖節，沒什麼好怕的，”我安慰自己，試圖放慢呼吸。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d7bec823 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:222
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7d11049:

    # man "Then I looked up at my house, hearing demonic laughter from the man’s direction." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7d11049
    man "然後我抬頭看向我的房子，聽到那個男人方向傳來的惡魔般的笑聲。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e7d11049 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:223
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2999497f:

    # man "An icicle of terror stabbed at my heart." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2999497f
    man "恐懼的冰柱刺入我的心。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2999497f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:227
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d608c514:

    # man "There, in my daughter’s window, flickering softly, was a candle." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d608c514
    man "在我女兒的窗戶裡，柔和閃爍著一根蠟燭。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d608c514 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:232
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_1:

    # "They suddenly turn towards you. Their mouth turned up into a warm grin. Their eyes sinister." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_1
    "他們突然轉向你。他們的嘴角露出溫暖的微笑。眼神陰險。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:245
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1bea3c92:

    # man "You are taking a shower." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1bea3c92
    man "你正在洗澡。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1bea3c92 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:247
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d68c5057:

    # man "It’s not the type of shower you take before a job interview, maybe aiming for your cleanliness to impress somebody or someone supposedly worthy of impressing, nor is it the type of shower you take after a long workout at the gym or after a jog, or after whatever it is that applies to you." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d68c5057
    man "這不是你在面試前洗的那種澡，可能是為了讓你的清潔給某人或某個值得讓人印象深刻的人留下印象，也不是你在健身房長時間鍛煉或慢跑後洗的那種澡，或者是適合你的任何情況。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d68c5057 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:252
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c23f74e5:

    # man "No, you’re in your bathroom right now, standing under the soothing beam of hot water with wisps of steam spiraling off of your back." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c23f74e5
    man "不，你現在就在你的浴室裡，站在熱水的舒緩光束下，水蒸氣從你的背上盤旋而起。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c23f74e5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:254
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_017fd8c9:

    # man "Because you’ve got nothing better to do tonight, and you like that squeaky-clean feeling before hitting the hay, and, although this isn’t your first shower today, at least you can sleep easy knowing you’re cleansed of the day’s many stresses." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_017fd8c9
    man "因為今晚你沒有更好的事情可以做，你喜歡在睡覺前那種乾淨的感覺，雖然這不是你今天的第一次洗澡，但至少你可以安心入睡，知道你已經清除了這一天的許多壓力。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_017fd8c9 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:259
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_35e7c9f6:

    # man "Soap." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_35e7c9f6
    man "肥皂。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_35e7c9f6 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:261
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cbe6a3d7:

    # man "Shampoo." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cbe6a3d7
    man "洗髮水。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cbe6a3d7 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:263
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e770d66c:

    # man "It’s all there, but you don’t so much as touch it." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e770d66c
    man "都在那裡，但你連碰都不碰。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e770d66c # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:265
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e5c7e12e:

    # man "For now you’re just letting the water’s steam filter through your pores, and enjoying the simplicity of it all." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e5c7e12e
    man "現在你只是讓水的蒸汽滲透到你的毛孔中，享受這一切的簡單。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e5c7e12e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:267
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0e3e5b8a:

    # man "The lights go out." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0e3e5b8a
    man "燈熄了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0e3e5b8a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:269
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b86c1a6a:

    # man "Startled, your feet squeal on the floor of the shower and you pause to make sure the sound was from your own." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b86c1a6a
    man "你被驚嚇到，腳在淋浴間的地板上發出尖叫聲，你停下來確保那聲音是你自己的。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b86c1a6a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:271
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e182d824:

    # man "The sound of water hitting the floor in the dark." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e182d824
    man "水打在地板上的聲音在黑暗中。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e182d824 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:273
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_18e8008b:

    # man "You feel as if you’re not alone in the room. Which is impossible, because you’re the only one in the house." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_18e8008b
    man "你覺得房間裡好像不止你一個人。這是不可能的，因為你是房子裡唯一的人。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_18e8008b # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:275
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_40979a4e:

    # man "The sound of the switch had been unmistakable." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_40979a4e
    man "開關的聲音是無可錯認的。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_40979a4e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:277
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31674d6e:

    # man "You stay under it, under the water, your one and only landmark." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31674d6e
    man "你待在水下，水是你唯一的地標。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31674d6e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:279
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_232b6ba5:

    # man "Feeling around, your hands meet the slippery shower tiles, and you feel like a mime trapped in a blank box as you fumble for the adjacent wall, then grab the curtain, finally something real, something you can touch that’s now in front of you and will stay static as you reclaim your bearings." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_232b6ba5
    man "摸索著，你的手碰到了滑溜溜的淋浴瓷磚，你感覺像是一個被困在空白盒子裡的啞劇演員，摸索著旁邊的牆壁，然後抓住窗簾，終於有了真實的東西，一個你可以觸摸的東西，現在就在你面前，當你重新找回方向時會保持靜止。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_232b6ba5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:284
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a83f57e7:

    # man "Outside of the shower, something starts choking." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a83f57e7
    man "淋浴外面，有東西開始窒息。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a83f57e7 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:286
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_904d6b3d:

    # man "You abruptly stop breathing. Strain to hear." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_904d6b3d
    man "你突然停止呼吸。努力聽。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_904d6b3d # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:289
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a1cb5b19:

    # man "It’s a gut-wrenching cough that wheezes in and out, and your hand freezes before recoiling back to your torso in shock." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a1cb5b19
    man "那是一種令人痛苦的咳嗽，呼吸聲時斷時續，你的手僵住了，然後震驚地縮回到你的軀幹。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a1cb5b19 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:291
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f410a257:

    # man "And in the middle of the bathwater rain noisily splashing by your feet, you hear its footsteps inching closer as it struggles to breathe." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f410a257
    man "在你腳下嘩啦啦的洗澡水中，你聽到它的腳步聲在逼近，它掙扎著呼吸。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f410a257 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:293
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c37b6dfd:

    # man "The thump of pads on the floor stepping closer." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c37b6dfd
    man "墊子在地板上的聲音越來越近。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c37b6dfd # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:295
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_90cdb521:

    # man "You can do nothing but press your back against the wet wall behind you in paralysis, to the point where the sounds are less than a foot away from where you remember the curtain to be, at your own eye level." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_90cdb521
    man "你只能在癱瘓中把背靠在你身後的濕牆上，聽到聲音距離你記得的窗簾不到一英尺，正好在你的眼睛水平。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_90cdb521 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:298
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1d02148d:

    # man "That’s when the lights come on and the choking stops." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1d02148d
    man "就在這時，燈亮了，窒息聲停止了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1d02148d # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:300
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f9c132b6:

    # man "You shut off the water." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f9c132b6
    man "你關掉水。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f9c132b6 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:302
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d4f81874:

    # man "All is quiet and you look to either side just in case, remembering all the horror movies you’ve seen in your entire life at this moment." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d4f81874
    man "一切都安靜下來，你左右看了看，以防萬一，這時你想起了你一生中看過的所有恐怖電影。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d4f81874 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:304
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f850bd1:

    # man "Not a sound except the gurgling of the drain at your toes, sucking down the last of the water calmly like it had all been in your head and none of it had happened." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f850bd1
    man "除了你腳趾的排水口在吸走最後的水流時發出的咕嚕聲，沒有其他聲音，就像這一切都在你的腦海中，什麼都沒發生過。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f850bd1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:306
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_14501f3e:

    # man "You’re standing there, dripping wet and naked, when you realize you’ve got to step out and meet whatever’s there, waiting on the other side of the curtain." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_14501f3e
    man "你站在那裡，濕淋淋的，赤裸著，當你意識到你必須走出去面對窗簾另一邊的任何東西時。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_14501f3e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:312
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_2:

    # "They suddenly turn towards you. Their mouth turned up into a warm grin. Their eyes sinister." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_2
    "他們突然轉向你。他們的嘴角露出溫暖的微笑。眼神陰險。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_2 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:324
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9ec23ab7:

    # girl "It was hardly past seven that morning when the Gravedigger saw the Earth stir. Fingers, rotted and skeletal, burst forth from the dirt, and with force they pulled their bodies to freedom." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9ec23ab7
    girl "那天早上才剛過七點，掘墓者就看到大地在顫動。腐爛的骷髏手指從泥土中爆出，並用力將他們的身體拉向自由。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9ec23ab7 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:327
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f467aeb8:

    # girl "It was happening all over the graveyard. Every grave. Every square inch of dirt was overturned." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f467aeb8
    girl "整個墓地都在發生這種情況。每一個墳墓。每一寸泥土都被翻動。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f467aeb8 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:331
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_004a140a:

    # girl "Soon, there were thousands; so many more than the graveyard actually held. A horde of the undead stood before him." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_004a140a
    girl "很快，數以千計的……比墓地實際容納的還要多。亡靈的群體站在他面前。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_004a140a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:334
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_69cb1a78:

    # girl "The Gravedigger watched, with his shovel in hand." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_69cb1a78
    girl "掘墓者手握鐵鍬觀看著。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_69cb1a78 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:336
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f33bf24:

    # girl "He found himself simultaneously horrified and fascinated. The creatures stumbled about. They moved with urgency, but their decrepit bodies only allowed for so much. Yelling and screaming, they started to coalesce near the center of the graveyard." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f33bf24
    girl "他發現自己同時感到恐懼和著迷。那些生物在蹣跚而行。他們動作急切，但他們的殘破身體只能做到這樣。他們叫喊著，尖叫著，開始在墓地的中心聚集。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f33bf24 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:341
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f4b8705:

    # girl "They were revolting, damned souls." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f4b8705
    girl "他們是令人厭惡的，被詛咒的靈魂。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_8f4b8705 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:343
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05d07300:

    # girl "Just as the Gravedigger went to turn, to flee, a hand gripped his shoulder. The grime soaked deep into his sleeve. It leaked down his arm." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05d07300
    girl "就在掘墓者準備轉身逃跑時，一隻手抓住了他的肩膀。污垢深深滲入他的袖子，沿著他的手臂流下。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_05d07300 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:347
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1945723e:

    # girl "Behind him, a man (what was left of him) stared into the Gravedigger’s eyes. The corpse’s face had long since lost its tissue, but it had eyes, returned anew to their sockets, that showed nothing but fear." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1945723e
    girl "在他身後，一個男人（他剩下的部分）盯著掘墓者的眼睛。屍體的臉早已失去了組織，但它的眼睛重新回到眼窩中，顯示出恐懼。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1945723e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:350
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_48b823e1:

    # girl "The ghoul spoke to the Gravedigger, and the Gravedigger listened." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_48b823e1
    girl "那個幽靈對掘墓者說話，而掘墓者聽著。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_48b823e1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:352
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f39b8f60:

    # girl "“Go,” It begged of him. “Please. Go.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f39b8f60
    girl "“走吧，”它懇求他。“拜託。走吧。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f39b8f60 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:354
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4f05502f:

    # girl "What sort of madness was this? What trickery of Hell?" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4f05502f
    girl "這是什麼瘋狂？地獄的什麼詭計？" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4f05502f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:357
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e9a2c332:

    # girl "The Gravedigger brought his shovel to bear, and he swung it down on the corpse. It was met with a revolting, moist crunch. The figure fell. His fingers twitched, and his skull leaked." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e9a2c332
    girl "掘墓者舉起鐵鍬，朝屍體揮去。它發出令人作嘔的濕潤的嘎吱聲。那個身影倒下了。他的手指顫動，頭骨流出液體。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e9a2c332 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:361
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_26c96823:

    # girl "From behind, three more figures came. Two ignored the Gravedigger. They bent to pick up the wounded husk at the Gravedigger’s feet." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_26c96823
    girl "從後面，三個身影走來。兩個忽視了掘墓者。他們彎下腰把掘墓者腳下受傷的軀殼撿起來。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_26c96823 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:365
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d26c892e:

    # girl "They dragged him on with all the strength they could muster. They carried him like a wounded ally. The third figure, what had once been a woman, perhaps, spoke to the Gravedigger." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d26c892e
    girl "他們用盡全力把他拖走。他們像拖著一個受傷的盟友一樣拖著他。第三個身影，可能曾經是個女人，對掘墓者說話。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d26c892e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:369
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1cbb68d3:

    # girl "She pleaded." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1cbb68d3
    girl "她懇求道。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1cbb68d3 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:371
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3d10c809:

    # girl "“Go. Please. Tell them.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3d10c809
    girl "“走吧。拜託。告訴他們。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3d10c809 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:373
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_389b7f97:

    # girl "The Gravedigger couldn’t move. He wouldn’t." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_389b7f97
    girl "掘墓者動不了。他不會動。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_389b7f97 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:376
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d2308b1c:

    # girl "These fiends were no masters of him. Why did they command him so? For what purpose? Answers! He demanded answers!" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d2308b1c
    girl "這些惡魔不是他的主人。為什麼他們要命令他？為了什麼目的？答案！他要求答案！" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d2308b1c # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:382
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9636421a:

    # girl "“Why?” he asked, the words falling out of his bearded face. “Why aren’t you in the ground?”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9636421a
    girl "“為什麼？”他問道，話語從他蓄鬍的臉上掉落。“你們為什麼不在地裡？”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9636421a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:384
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_27a1db80:

    # girl "The ghoul didn’t blink. She simply told him the terrible truth." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_27a1db80
    girl "那個幽靈沒有眨眼。她只是告訴他可怕的真相。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_27a1db80 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:386
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9c760cc0:

    # girl "“Hell isn’t safe anymore.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9c760cc0
    girl "“地獄不再安全了。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_9c760cc0 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:388
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_71ce8887:

    # girl "Those words. The Gravedigger couldn’t even comprehend them. What was the meaning of them?" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_71ce8887
    girl "那些話。掘墓者甚至無法理解它們。它們的意義是什麼？" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_71ce8887 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:392
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12d6eee2:

    # girl "Hell? Safe? What kind of haven was the pit of eternal damnation?" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12d6eee2
    girl "地獄？安全？永恆詛咒之坑是什麼樣的避風港？" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12d6eee2 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:396
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b9974868:

    # girl "“What are you talking about?”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b9974868
    girl "“你在說什麼？”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b9974868 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:398
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2edd16ff:

    # girl "Had she a tear to cry she would have let it fall. Instead, she had to use her trembling voice to convey her fears." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2edd16ff
    girl "如果她有眼淚，她會讓它流下。相反，她必須用顫抖的聲音來傳達她的恐懼。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2edd16ff # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:401
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e17f8ce4:

    # girl "“Lucifer is dead. He killed Him. He is coming.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e17f8ce4
    girl "“路西法死了。他殺了他。他來了。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e17f8ce4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:403
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_445824a0:

    # girl "The words held no meaning for the Gravedigger, for he had not been there. He had not seen the horrors that even the denizens of Hell itself couldn’t describe." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_445824a0
    girl "這些話對掘墓者來說毫無意義，因為他不在那裡。他沒有看到即使是地獄的居民也無法描述的恐怖。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_445824a0 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:406
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_61cfe24a:

    # girl "Then, from the graves, dark figures with eyes of flame and hatred came. They moved like smoke, and they filled the air with their sulfurous fumes." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_61cfe24a
    girl "然後，從墳墓中，帶著火焰和仇恨的黑色身影來了。他們像煙霧一樣移動，空氣中充滿了他們的硫磺煙霧。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_61cfe24a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:409
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d3a361d1:

    # girl "The Gravedigger watched as demons, Satan’s orchestrators of pain and suffering, began to assist the poor, wandering souls below." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d3a361d1
    girl "掘墓者看著惡魔，撒旦的痛苦和折磨的策劃者，開始幫助下面可憐的流浪靈魂。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_d3a361d1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:411
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7298132:

    # girl "They started to stack atop each other. One by one, their bodies built the foundation." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7298132
    girl "他們開始一個接一個地堆疊。他們的身體建造了基礎。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_b7298132 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:413
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ce0205a:

    # girl "What in the name of God? He could only ponder." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ce0205a
    girl "這是什麼上帝的名義？他只能思考。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ce0205a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:415
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_57a041a9:

    # girl "A collective lamenting cascaded down from the hills around. The Gravedigger saw them." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_57a041a9
    girl "從周圍的山丘傳來集體的哀嘆。掘墓者看到了他們。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_57a041a9 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:417
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b74c567:

    # girl "From every direction more hordes moved together. More undead. They lumbered forth, with his cemetery in their sights. Their hellish rendezvous." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b74c567
    girl "從四面八方更多的群體聚集在一起。更多的亡靈。他們朝著他的墓地前進。他們的地獄聚集地。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b74c567 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:422
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c0ce442:

    # girl "The Gravedigger was speechless." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c0ce442
    girl "掘墓者無言以對。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c0ce442 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:424
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_de1658a4:

    # girl "The ghoul instructed him." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_de1658a4
    girl "幽靈指示他。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_de1658a4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:426
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cd1eb694:

    # girl "“Go. To your family. We’ll need them too.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cd1eb694
    girl "“去。去找你的家人。我們也需要他們。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cd1eb694 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:429
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c1b1731f:

    # girl "“My—” he questioned the request, “My family?”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c1b1731f
    girl "“我的——”他質疑這個要求，“我的家人？”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c1b1731f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:431
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebc3c19d:

    # girl "“The living,” the thing corrected, her gaze skyward. “We’ll need them too, if we are to make it.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebc3c19d
    girl "“活著的人，”那東西糾正道，她的目光向天空。“如果我們要成功，我們也需要他們。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ebc3c19d # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:434
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c5b2870e:

    # girl "“Make it? Where?”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c5b2870e
    girl "“成功？去哪裡？”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c5b2870e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:436
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0cd608b7:

    # girl "The ghoul cried as she wandered forth. Urgency flooded her words." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0cd608b7
    girl "幽靈哭泣著向前走去。她的話語中充滿了緊迫感。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0cd608b7 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:439
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2fa41815:

    # girl "“The gates! We have to make it to the gates.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2fa41815
    girl "“大門！我們必須到達大門。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_2fa41815 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:441
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_36f4fa19:

    # girl "The Gravedigger shook his head. Their aim was clear, but his teachings were concrete." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_36f4fa19
    girl "掘墓者搖了搖頭。他們的目標很明確，但他的教義是堅定的。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_36f4fa19 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:444
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc821e84:

    # girl "“What’s judged is judged. He won’t take you, or any of us unworthy.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc821e84
    girl "“被審判的就是被審判的。他不會接受你們，或者我們任何不配的人。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc821e84 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:446
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5e732d48:

    # girl "That stopped her, if for just a moment. She turned, for he knew nothing." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5e732d48
    girl "這讓她停下了，哪怕只是片刻。她轉身，因為他什麼都不知道。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5e732d48 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:448
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ef33908:

    # girl "“We seek not redemption,” she said. “We damned seek to warn the righteous.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ef33908
    girl "“我們不尋求救贖，”她說。“我們被詛咒的人尋求警告正義的人。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ef33908 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:451
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5d57870a:

    # girl "The honesty in the ghoul’s voice brought a heavy weight to the Gravedigger’s stomach." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5d57870a
    girl "幽靈聲音中的誠實給掘墓者的胃帶來了沉重的壓力。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_5d57870a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:453
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31a0696f:

    # girl "He couldn’t stand. The Earth below had started to tremble." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31a0696f
    girl "他站不起來。地面開始震動。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_31a0696f # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:456
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ded48d40:

    # girl "The Gravedigger fell to the dirt as his knees gave in, and with his face to the ground, he heard it." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ded48d40
    girl "掘墓者跪倒在地，當他的膝蓋屈服時，他的臉朝著地面，他聽到了。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_ded48d40 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:458
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12b4d4bd:

    # girl "There was a deep, unbridled scream echoing below the surface. A demented laugh. The sound of a thousand hornet wings, and insect feet." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12b4d4bd
    girl "地面下有一聲深沉、無拘無束的尖叫。瘋狂的笑聲。成千上萬的黃蜂翅膀和昆蟲腳的聲音。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_12b4d4bd # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:462
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fa3d1303:

    # girl "It grew closer. Climbing." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fa3d1303
    girl "它越來越近了。正在攀爬。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_fa3d1303 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:465
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bccf6ed5:

    # girl "As he stood, bodies were flung atop each other, as the demons and the forgotten built their tower to salvation." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bccf6ed5
    girl "當他站起來時，屍體被扔在一起，惡魔和被遺忘的人建造了他們的救贖之塔。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bccf6ed5 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:467
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_787fdce8:

    # girl "“Who is He?” The Gravedigger asked. It was his turn to plead, but the corpses said nothing." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_787fdce8
    girl "“他是誰？”掘墓者問道。輪到他懇求了，但屍體什麼也沒說。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_787fdce8 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:470
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_768d5a1c:

    # girl "It didn’t take much for the Gravedigger to realize that they couldn’t respond even if they wanted to." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_768d5a1c
    girl "掘墓者很快就意識到，即使他們想回答，他們也無法回答。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_768d5a1c # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:472
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3c64ac45:

    # girl "They didn’t know." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3c64ac45
    girl "他們不知道。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_3c64ac45 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:474
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_88487ea3:

    # girl "As the Gravedigger ran home, the ghoul uttered a final mantra under her breath." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_88487ea3
    girl "當掘墓者跑回家時，幽靈在她的呼吸中低聲說著最後的咒語。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_88487ea3 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:476
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c3bf306:

    # girl "The words still tasted so alien to her, so vile and disgusting. It was all they had left." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c3bf306
    girl "這些話對她來說仍然如此陌生，如此可憎和噁心。這是他們唯一剩下的。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0c3bf306 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:479
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_37d4cf66:

    # girl "“God must know that He is coming.”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_37d4cf66
    girl "“上帝必須知道他來了。”" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_37d4cf66 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:485
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_3:

    # "They suddenly turn towards you. Their mouth turned up into a warm grin. Their eyes sinister." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_3
    "他們突然轉向你。他們的嘴角露出溫暖的微笑。眼神陰險。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_3 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:496
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1503e9ec:

    # man "Here I lay, all snuggled up in bed, warm and satisfied under the soft silk covers, watching some stupid documentary on TV I’d never heard of." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1503e9ec
    man "我躺在這裡，舒舒服服地躺在床上，滿足地躺在柔軟的絲綢被子下，看著電視上我從未聽說過的一個愚蠢的紀錄片。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1503e9ec # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:498
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e1f7cf3e:

    # man "I’d turn it over, but the gallon tub of cookie dough ice cream wouldn’t let me use my hands for anything other than shoveling the frozen treat into my mouth." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e1f7cf3e
    man "我想換台，但一加侖的餅乾麵團冰淇淋不讓我用手做其他事情，只能把冷凍的美味一勺一勺地送進嘴裡。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e1f7cf3e # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:500
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cb3e9bcd:

    # man "Nights like these are rare, it isn’t often that everyone’s out of the house but me, so I make sure to savour them, in fact, I wasn’t expecting anyone back till the morning." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cb3e9bcd
    man "這樣的夜晚很少見，並不是經常只有我一個人在家，所以我確保珍惜它們，事實上，我本來預計到早上都不會有人回來。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_cb3e9bcd # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:502
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bef205f1:

    # man "That’s what made the sound of the door opening downstairs so alarming." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bef205f1
    man "這就是為什麼樓下門開的聲音如此令人震驚。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bef205f1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:504
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_031dd710:

    # man "Panic hits me like a steam train, I silently leap out from under the covers, spilling the ice cream all over the pristine white carpet on the floor, and creak open the wardrobe next to the bed." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_031dd710
    man "恐慌像蒸汽火車一樣襲擊我，我靜靜地從被子下跳出來，把冰淇淋灑在地板上潔白的地毯上，輕輕地打開床旁的衣櫃。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_031dd710 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:506
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_78f96296:

    # man "I hear footsteps, heavy and indiscreet, like they want me to know they’re here." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_78f96296
    man "我聽到腳步聲，沉重而明顯，就像他們想讓我知道他們在這裡一樣。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_78f96296 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:508
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_396504ac:

    # man "I pant, and pick up the spoon I had just been using to enjoy a relaxing night." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_396504ac
    man "我喘著氣，拿起剛才用來享受輕鬆夜晚的勺子。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_396504ac # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:510
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a2ad18cd:

    # man "The footsteps get louder, I force myself into the miniscule space remaining in the wardrobe, and close the door, just as the stranger opens the bedroom door, not sparing any seconds for silence." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a2ad18cd
    man "腳步聲越來越大，我強迫自己進入衣櫃剩下的微小空間，關上門，就在陌生人打開臥室門的時候，沒有留下一絲靜音。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a2ad18cd # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:512
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c53f3b79:

    # man "I peer through the gap, his face looks familiar, but I can’t place my finger on where I know him from." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c53f3b79
    man "我透過縫隙窺視，他的臉看起來很熟悉，但我無法確定我在哪裡認識他。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_c53f3b79 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:514
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_00484368:

    # man "He spots the spilled ice cream, and darts his head across the wide expanse of the bedroom." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_00484368
    man "他看到了灑落的冰淇淋，迅速掃視了整個寬敞的臥室。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_00484368 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:516
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_82338b32:

    # man "“Hello?” he calls, not sounding vicious, but I’ve made that mistake before." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_82338b32
    man "“喂？”他喊道，聽起來並不惡意，但我以前犯過這個錯誤。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_82338b32 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:518
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f709b382:

    # man "Never, under any circumstances, assume friendliness from a voice." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f709b382
    man "無論在任何情況下，都不要從聲音中假設友好。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_f709b382 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:520
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9c18f42:

    # man "He looks under the bed. Oh crap, he’s looking for someone." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9c18f42
    man "他看了一下床底。哦，糟糕，他在找人。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_a9c18f42 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:522
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ac3ef21:

    # man "I hold back a whimper, and start bending the bowl of the spoon back and forth, hoping to snap it off and create some way of defending myself." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ac3ef21
    man "我忍住一聲哽咽，開始來回彎曲勺子的碗，希望能把它折斷，創造出某種自衛的方法。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_1ac3ef21 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:524
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_93f0cbd4:

    # man "It snaps, but it creates a metallic click, the man turns his head around, and makes his way to the wardrobe, I’m shaking now." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_93f0cbd4
    man "它斷了，但發出金屬的咔嗒聲，那人轉過頭，走向衣櫃，我現在正在顫抖。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_93f0cbd4 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:526
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0160ed1a:

    # man "Please don’t open it, please don’t open it, please don’t open it!" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0160ed1a
    man "請不要打開它，請不要打開它，請不要打開它！" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_0160ed1a # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:528
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc7f11a1:

    # man "The door swings open, and he sees me, we scream simultaneously in fear and surprise." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc7f11a1
    man "門猛地打開，他看到了我，我們同時驚恐地尖叫。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_bc7f11a1 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:530
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_33df57b9:

    # man "Without hesitation, I leap onto the man, and start digging into whatever stretch of flesh I can with the sharp edge of the spoon handle, he screeches in clear pain, but I won’t stop, I hammer the handle deep into his chest and neck, over and over, till he becomes motionless." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_33df57b9
    man "毫不猶豫地，我跳到那人身上，開始用勺柄的鋒利邊緣挖掘我能挖到的任何一塊肉，他尖叫著顯然的痛苦，但我不會停下來，我把柄深深地插入他的胸部和脖子，一遍又一遍，直到他變得一動不動。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_33df57b9 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:532
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_020b5b72:

    # man "I’ve killed him." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_020b5b72
    man "我殺了他。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_020b5b72 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:534
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b1b13df:

    # man "I cry in disgust, and sprint downstairs and away from the house, I charge down the road until I feel like I’m far enough away." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b1b13df
    man "我哭著感到噁心，衝下樓，遠離房子，我沿著路狂奔，直到我覺得自己已經足夠遠。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_6b1b13df # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:536
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_dfc898f6:

    # man "I sit down for a moment, and exhale heavily before regaining my composure." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_dfc898f6
    man "我坐下片刻，重重地呼出一口氣，然後重新恢復鎮定。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_dfc898f6 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:538
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e817b734:

    # man "Pulling out my phone, I open social media and search #party, hopefully this time, I’ll find a household that isn’t lying when they say they’ll be out all night." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e817b734
    man "拿出手機，我打開社交媒體，搜索#派對，希望這次，我能找到一個說他們會整晚外出的家庭。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_e817b734 # TL # Victorius - AI

# game/events/dreams/recurring_nightmare.rpy:543
translate chinese_traditional d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_4:

    # "They suddenly turn towards you. Their mouth turned up into a warm grin. Their eyes sinister." id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_4
    "他們突然轉向你。他們的嘴角露出溫暖的微笑。眼神陰險。" id d_Recurring_Nightmare_1_part2_4ac660d1_4 # TL # Victorius - AI

